@startuml
title Fortuna - Dashboard Query Flow

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as Frontend
participant "DashboardController" as Controller
participant "GetDashboardQueryHandler" as Handler
participant "DashboardReadRepository" as Repo
database "FortunaReadDb" as ReadDb

User -> Frontend : Open dashboard
Frontend -> Controller : GET /api/dashboard/{customerId}\nAuthorization: Bearer token
Controller -> Controller : Validate customerId from JWT
Controller -> Handler : GetDashboardQuery
Handler -> Repo : GetDashboardAsync(customerId)
Repo -> ReadDb : Load ProductTile list
Repo -> ReadDb : Load TimelineEvent list
Repo -> Repo : Compute total balance
Repo --> Handler : DashboardDto
Handler --> Controller : DashboardDto
Controller --> Frontend : DashboardResponse

note right of Repo
  Dashboard reads only from FortunaReadDb,
  not directly from the transactional write model.
end note

@enduml
